# Gogo Package And Feature Index

Use this rule as the first stop when an AI agent needs to discover which Gogo
package, CLI command, or generated project file owns a feature. This project
does not assume any external Codex memory. The local `.agent/rules/gogo/*`
files and public Gogo docs are the source of truth for framework usage.

Framework module: `github.com/cybersaksham/gogo`.

Never import `github.com/cybersaksham/gogo/internal` from this client project.
Use public packages only. When exact symbols or options are needed, run:

```bash
go doc github.com/cybersaksham/gogo/<package>
```

